    {
        "chapter_number": 14,
        "name": "ब्रह्मस्तुतिः",
        "name_transliterated": "Brahma-stutiḥ",
        "name_meaning": "Brahmā's Prayers to Lord Kṛṣṇa",
        "name_translation": "Brahmā's Prayers to Lord Kṛṣṇa",
        "verses_count": 61,
        "chapter_summary": "In this chapter, Śukadeva Gosvāmī continues to narrate the transcendental activities of Lord Kṛṣṇa. Details are covered in the pastimes of 'Brahmā's Prayers to Lord Kṛṣṇa', depicting how the Lord protects His devotees, establishes righteousness, and delights the residents of Vraja and Dvārakā.",
        "chapter_summary_hindi": "इस अध्याय में, शुकदेव गोस्वामी भगवान कृष्ण की दिव्य लीलाओं का वर्णन जारी रखते हैं। इसमें 'Brahmā's Prayers to Lord Kṛṣṇa' के अंतर्गत कृष्ण की दिव्य लीलाओं, भक्तों की रक्षा, और धर्म की स्थापना का सुंदर चित्रण किया गया है।",
