        "name_translation": "The Killing of Dhenukāsura",
        "verses_count": 43,
        "chapter_summary": "In this chapter, Śukadeva Gosvāmī continues to narrate the transcendental activities of Lord Kṛṣṇa. Details are covered in the pastimes of 'The Killing of Dhenukāsura', depicting how the Lord protects His devotees, establishes righteousness, and delights the residents of Vraja and Dvārakā.",
